## Setup (local)
1. Clone repo
2. Create `.env` with GOOGLE_API_KEY and SERPAPI_API_KEY
3. python -m venv venv && venv\Scripts\activate
4. pip install -r requirements.txt
5. uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8080
6. Open Swagger at: http://localhost:8080/docs

## Endpoint
POST /generate-post
Body: { "topic": "Artificial Intelligence" }

Response:
{
  "topic": "Artificial Intelligence",
  "news_sources": [...],
  "linkedin_post": "...",
  "image_suggestion": null
}
